# DMC Travel OS

# Data Dictionary

## Purpose

This document describes every database entity, field, data type and business meaning.

---

# Global Rules

Every business table contains:

* id (UUID)
* tenant_id (UUID)
* created_at
* updated_at
* created_by
* updated_by

Primary Key = UUID

---

